data.title: Nancy Ajram - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Nancy Ajram: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Arabic pop artist whose 2010 album 7 sold eight million copies worldwide. She has won three World Music Awards throughout her career. She is also a Goodwill Ambassador for UNICEF and has served as a judge on The Voice Kids Arabia since 2016.

Before Fame

She made her first television appearance at age twelve on the series Noujoun Al-Moustakbal. Her breakout single was "Akhasmak Ah."

Trivia

Her albums have reached Platinum certification in Lebanon, Egypt, Jordan, Algeria, and Tunisia.

Family Life

She married Dr. Fadi El Hachem in 2008; the couple have daughters named Mila, Ella and Lya.
